text: The 2015 Supercopa Centroamericana was an announced two-legged football match- up scheduled to be played in July and August 2015 between C.S. Cartaginés, winners of the 2014 Costa Rican Cup, and C.D. Olimpia, winners of the 2015 Honduran Cup.Cartagines.cr – Oficial: Cartaginés y Olimpia disputarán la Súper Copa Centroamericana – 29 May 2015 It was intended to be the first edition of the competition; however, without further explanation from the organizers, the matches were never played. ==Match details== ===First leg=== ===Second leg=== ==See also== *2014 Costa Rican Cup *2015 Honduran Cup ==References== 2015 Category:2015–16 in Costa Rican football Category:2015–16 in Honduran football
title: 2015 Supercopa Centroamericana
